OL,3,CTaliban has deliberately deprived 1.4m
OL,4,Cgirls of schooling, says UNESCO
OL,6,FThe Taliban has deliberately deprived
OL,7,F1.4 million Afghan girls of schooling
OL,8,Fthrough bans, UNESCO said on Thursday.
OL,10,FAfghanistan is the only country in the
OL,11,Fworld that bans female secondary and
OL,12,Fhigher education.
OL,14,FThe Taliban, which rose to power
OL,15,Fexactly three years ago in August
OL,16,F2021, barred education for girls above
OL,17,Fsixth grade (year seven) because it
OL,18,Fsaid it didn't comply with their
OL,19,Finterpretation of Sharia, or Islamic
OL,20,Flaw.
