OL,3,CTaliban has deliberately deprived 1.4m
OL,4,Cgirls of schooling, says UNESCO
OL,6,FThere is no ban for boys and the group
OL,7,Fshows no sign of taking the steps
OL,8,Fneeded to reopen classrooms and
OL,9,Fcampuses for girls and women.
OL,11,FUNESCO said that the number of girls
OL,12,Fdenied access to education increased
OL,13,Fby 300,000 since April 2023.
