OL,3,CTaliban has deliberately deprived 1.4m
OL,4,Cgirls of schooling, says UNESCO
OL,6,F"If we add the girls who were already
OL,7,Fout of school before the bans were
OL,8,Fintroduced, there are now almost 2.5
OL,9,Fmillion girls in the country deprived
OL,10,Fof their right to education,
OL,11,Frepresenting 80% of Afghan school-age
OL,12,Fgirls," UNESCO said.
OL,14,FAccess to primary education has also
OL,15,Ffallen since the Taliban took power in
OL,16,F2021, with 1.1 million fewer girls and
OL,17,Fboys attending school, according to
OL,18,FUNESCO data.
