OL,3,CTaliban has deliberately deprived 1.4m
OL,4,Cgirls of schooling, says UNESCO
OL,6,F"UNESCO is alarmed by the harmful
OL,7,Fconsequences of this increasingly
OL,8,Fmassive drop-out rate, which could
OL,9,Flead to a rise in child labor and
OL,10,Fearly marriage," it said.
OL,12,FAlison Davidian, the UN Women
OL,13,Frepresentative in Afghanistan, said in
OL,14,Fa post on X: "We cannot leave Afghan
OL,15,Fwomen to fight alone. If we do, we
OL,16,Fhave no moral ground to fight for
OL,17,Fwomen's rights anywhere."
