OL,6,FOne woman, Nasima, said to Davidian:
OL,7,F"I was married at 16. I couldn't
OL,8,Ffinish school. My hope was that my
OL,9,Fdaughter's life would be better. Now
OL,10,FI'm worried her life is going to be
OL,11,Fworse. To those who are still
OL,12,Flistening to our voices, please help
OL,13,Fus fight for our freedom."
